Excuse me.

06:21.800 --> 06:23.245
What?

06:23.360 --> 06:25.260
Oh.

06:25.360 --> 06:26.660
Hi, how are you?

06:26.760 --> 06:29.127
I'm fine, thanks. Are these your shoes?

06:29.240 --> 06:30.660
What? Yeah, yeah, they're my shoes.

06:30.760 --> 06:32.700
I didn't want to, you know,
mess up the car...

06:32.800 --> 06:34.140
