06:53.600 --> 06:55.860
It's no problem.

06:55.960 --> 06:57.340
Can I help you today?

06:57.440 --> 06:59.940
I'd like to buy a car.

07:00.040 --> 07:01.500
Cadillac, you know?

07:01.600 --> 07:03.180
Great.

07:03.280 --> 07:05.487
