07:11.800 --> 07:14.644
- Wow.
- My personal favorite.

07:21.400 --> 07:22.700
What do you think?

07:22.800 --> 07:24.211
I don't know.

07:26.720 --> 07:28.802
Well, take your time,
there's no pressure.

07:30.080 --> 07:32.606
Blue is a very calm color.

07:42.080 --> 07:44.940
